# UX Flow Rules

## List Page

- Show:
  - search
  - filter
  - create button

- Click row → detail page

---

## Create Page

- Empty form
- Focus on Title first
- Auto generate Slug

---

## Edit Page

- Pre-fill data
- Show last updated

---

## Detail Page

- Display:
  - title
  - content
  - tags
  - stats

- Tabs:
  - Info
  - SEO
  - Analytics

---

## Feedback

- After save → success toast
- After delete → confirm dialog